			figure.fragment
				img.height-320(src=imgAssets+'door_hellblade.jpg')
				p Hellblade - window element
+frameInbox('9. Revisiting')
	div
		ul
			li.fragment Is there any reason to revisit already visited areas?
		.space-xl
		.flex-cols-3.fill
			figure.fragment
				img.height-320(src=imgAssets+'revisit_rayman.jpg')
				p Rayman - after character development
			figure.fragment
				img.height-320(src=imgAssets+'revisit_darksouls.jpg')
				p Dark Souls - "I'm lost again!"
			figure.fragment
				img.height-320(src=imgAssets+'revisit_openworld.jpg')
				p Open world games - quests
				.tip.absolute.fragment.fade-in-then-out
					img.height-550(src=globalAssets+'memes/quests.jpg')
+frameInbox('10. Randomness')
	div
		ul
			li.fragment How the game works with randomness?
		.space-xl
		.flex-cols-3.fill
			figure.fragment
				img.height-320(src=imgAssets+'random_tetris.jpg')
				p Tetris - random permutations
			figure.fragment
				img.height-320(src=imgAssets+'random_pokemon.jpg')
				p Pokémon series - random encounter
				.tip.absolute.fragment.fade-in-then-out
					img.height-500(src=globalAssets+'memes/miss.jpg')
			figure.fragment
				img.height-320(src=imgAssets+'retro_gwars.jpg')
				p Geometry Wars - random waves